          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3834">
            <h1 id="minister-of-state-for-international-development">Minister of State for International Development</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<ul>
  <li>Caribbean</li>
  <li>Overseas Territories</li>
  <li>United Nations and Commonwealth</li>
  <li>International financial institutions</li>
  <li>Europe and trade</li>
  <li>Economic development and CDC</li>
  <li>Cross Government Fund (Prosperity)</li>
  <li>Global partnerships</li>
  <li>Inclusive Societies: disability, gender, ageing, faith, LGBT and VAWG</li>
  <li>Value for money, building on the Supplier Review, refining business case process and transparency releases</li>
  <li>Minister for Abercrombie House Minister, our joint headquarters in Scotland</li>
</ul>
